name: Ass-id lemon
description: ‘Ass-id lemon’ is about freeing yourself from judgment and finally accepting yourself more. It’s about embodying the bold look that the lemon represents and letting go. ‘Ass-id lemon’ is the second nft in the second part of the lemon collection. The second part of the lemon collection tells the rest of the story in 6 illustrations. This part is about becoming and sharing the lemon. Digital artwork made in 2021 by Camila Trapasso (camamblo).
